        <p class="lead">Data gathering is the principal pursuit of automation. BeeBit handles the people side. </p>
        
        <p>The project to create the BeeBit Hive first began when Nube iO identified limitations of their <abbr title="Heating, Ventilation and Air Conditioning">HVAC</abbr> automation systems, as collected data was missing a variable - people count. For NubeIO, this meant seeking an IoT solution to the problem to fit with their existing product line. BeeBit is an answer to this.</p>
